---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="AI Agents & Intelligent Automation | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="AI that saves you 15+ hours/week — email agents, lead routing & workflow automation. Built by a Seattle-based developer."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-950 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Text side -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">Spending Hours on Work a Machine Could Do in Minutes?</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">The boring, repetitive work is eating your week. Let's automate it.</p>
          <a href="/contact/?service=ai" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors text-lg">
            Request a Free Discovery Call →
          </a>
        </div>
        <!-- Image side -->
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/hero-ai.jpg" alt="AI-powered automation workflow with intelligent email agents and lead routing" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/10 w-full" />
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/20 to-teal-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-xl -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">The Problem</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">The Manual Work Is Eating Your Week</h2>
      <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>You're spending 20 hours a week on things that don't require a human brain — sorting emails, copying data between systems, writing the same responses over and over, manually routing inquiries. It's tedious, error-prone, and it's keeping you from the work that actually grows your business.</p>
        <p>Everyone's talking about AI, but most of it is chatbot demos and vaporware. The businesses winning with AI aren't the ones with the flashiest tools — they're the ones who automated the boring stuff.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">The Solution</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">AI That Works While You Sleep</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📧</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Email Agents</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">AI that reads, understands, and drafts responses to customer emails in the right tone, with the right information, at the right timing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Intelligent Lead Routing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">AI that scores incoming leads, categorizes inquiries, and routes them to the right workflow before you've finished your coffee.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⚙️</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Workflow Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Connect your systems with intelligent middleware. When X happens, do Y — but with the judgment to handle edge cases.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📝</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Content Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Blog post generation, SEO optimization, and social media scheduling — all coordinated through a single pipeline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔍</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Data Enrichment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Automatically pull in context about your customers and market to make every interaction more informed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📡</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-2">Smart Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">AI-powered system monitoring across your infrastructure. Know about problems before your customers do.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Results</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">Real Results from Production AI</h2>
      <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">For one client, we deployed AI email agents that:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
          <li>• Draft responses across <strong>two distinct brand personas</strong></li>
          <li>• Handle initial customer inquiries <strong>automatically</strong> — reducing response time to under 5 minutes</li>
          <li>• Save the owner <strong>15+ hours/week</strong> on email management alone</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/work/transportation-crm/" class="inline-block mt-4 text-blue-500 font-medium hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Read the full case study →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">FAQ</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group" open>
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Will the AI sound robotic?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">No. We train AI agents on your actual communication style. Clients can't tell the difference between an AI draft and one you wrote yourself.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            What if the AI makes a mistake?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">AI agents draft responses for your review — they don't send automatically (unless you want them to). You always have the final say.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do I need special software to use AI automation?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">No. AI agents work with the tools you already have — email, calendar, your CRM. No new software to learn.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 group">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy-950 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            How much can I realistically save?
            <span class="text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Most clients save 10-20 hours per week on manual processes. The ROI usually pays for the entire project within the first 2-3 months.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-4">Straightforward Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-2">Most AI projects: <span class="font-bold text-navy-950">$3,000 – $15,000</span></p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">Monthly maintenance available. Ongoing AI API costs outlined in your proposal.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Automate the Boring Stuff</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">Every project starts with a free discovery call. No commitment, no sales pitch.</p>
      <a href="/contact/?service=ai" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors min-h-[44px] text-lg">
        Request a Discovery Call
      </a>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <a href="/services/crm/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">CRM Development →</a>
        <a href="/services/web/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Web Development →</a>
        <a href="/services/cloud/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cloud & DevOps →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "itemListElement": [
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Services", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "AI Automation", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/ai/" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "@type": "ProfessionalService",
          "name": "AI Agents & Intelligent Automation — OpsHQ Digital",
          "url": "https://opshqdigital.com/services/ai/",
          "description": "AI email agents, lead routing, and workflow automation that saves 15+ hours per week.",
          "provider": { "@id": "https://opshqdigital.com/#organization" },
          "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Seattle", "addressRegion": "WA" },
          "priceRange": "$3,000 – $15,000"
        },
        {
          "@type": "FAQPage",
          "mainEntity": [
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "Will the AI sound robotic?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "No. We train AI agents on your actual communication style. Clients can't tell the difference between an AI draft and one you wrote yourself." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "What if the AI makes a mistake?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "AI agents draft responses for your review — they don't send automatically (unless you want them to). You always have the final say." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "Do I need special software to use AI automation?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "No. AI agents work with the tools you already have — email, calendar, your CRM. No new software to learn." }},
            { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much can I realistically save?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most clients save 10-20 hours per week on manual processes. The ROI usually pays for the entire project within the first 2-3 months." }}
          ]
        }
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
